            <p>Dubai is also known as the 'Pearl of the Gulf', 'Jewel of the world', and the 'City of Gold'. It is a modern and progressive city in the Middle East, famous for landmarks like the Burj Khalifa and Dubai Mall. Additionally, Dubai is known for its vibrant culture, luxurious infrastructure, and scorching summer heat.</p>
